<div type="definition">
<p>Be WICKED so as to LACK APPROPRIATE FAITHFULNESS.</p>
    <div type="definition" resp="#CH" modified="2023-09-13T01:29:36.238+09:00">
            <p>WICKED so as NOT to be LOYAL.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for disloyalty is èr 貳／二.</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>不忠</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
