                <note>
<p>UNTRUSTWORTHY</p>
<p>infidus refers to unworthiness of trust.</p>
<p>infidelis refers to someone who is unfaithful and therefore does not deserve any trust but is to be criticised for his actions.</p>
<p>perfidus refers to treacherousness not as a general characteristic but as demonstrated in specific actions.</p>
